show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: When Ava uncovers the ultimate betrayal—her boyfriend Ben and best friend Sarah's secret affair—she's consumed by a thirst for retribution. Enter Max, her unexpected ally in the art of revenge. Together, they orchestrate a brilliant scheme that slowly unravels the web of deception surrounding her former loved ones. Through calculated manipulations and cunning strategies, Ava pulls Ben and Sarah into an emotional labyrinth from which there seems no escape. As the tension escalates and shocking revelations emerge, both hunter and prey are forced to confront painful truths.
